Package: curl
Type: Package
Title: A Connection Interface to Libcurl.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-11-17
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: The curl() function provides a drop-in replacement for base url()
    with added support for https, http 2.0, sftp, and other libcurl goodies.
    This interface is implemented using the recent RConnection API in order to
    support incremental processing of binary streams. If you are looking for a
    simple HTTP client, have a look at the RCurl or httr packages instead.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: libcurl, OpenSSL (e.g: libcurl4-openssl-dev)
